      <biogHist id="md5-ccedfd36e7fa73242fcf708b8961eba3">
        <p>Author, [19--]- .  Darlene J. Comfort moved to Fort McMurray, Alberta in 1968.  In addition to several articles, she has published three books on the history of &lt;i&gt;Fort McMurray: Meeting Place of Many Waters: A History of Fort McMurray (1973-1974)&lt;/i&gt;, &lt;i&gt;Pass the McMurray Salt Please!&lt;/i&gt; (1975) and &lt;i&gt;The Abasand Fiasco: The Rise and Fall of a Brave Pioneer Oil Sands Extraction Plant&lt;/i&gt; (1980). This collection was gathered as research for her publications.</p>
      </biogHist>
